      "title": "When will I get my refund?",
      "slug": "when-will-i-get-my-refund",
      "content": "Refunds are processed within 24 hours of approval. Timeline by payment method:\n\n- UPI: 1-2 business days\n- Debit/Credit Card: 5-7 business days\n- Net Banking: 3-5 business days\n- Zipkart Wallet: Instant\n- COD: Bank transfer in 5-7 business days\n\nYou'll receive an SMS and email confirmation once processed.",
